# Calculate the Sum and Average of Elements

# Problem:
# Write a Python program that calculates and prints the total sum of all elements in an array and then calculates and prints the average of those elements.
# Goal: Learn how to perform arithmetic operations on arrays.

#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

listofnumber=[10,11,12,78,9,0]
sum=(sum(listofnumber))
print(sum)
avg=int(sum/len(listofnumber))
print(avg)

